"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Determining setup for library tests**\\n\\nFor the issue of fixing the native-image run for existing 1.5.0 tests under the new version 2.0-beta4, I don’t think extra setup is required beyond what's in the existing tests. However, the task asks for recommendations on setup before meaningful coverage can be reached. Even if existing tests have it, I see that the library does need the servlet API. Still, I should avoid restating deterministic entries as guidance and focus solely on the decision.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"action\": \"advisory_preparation\",\n  \"summary\": \"Jackrabbit WebDAV exposes servlet-based server/request/response APIs and declares javax.servlet:servlet-api as a provided dependency, so tests that meaningfully cover normal WebDAV server usage need the servlet API added explicitly.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [\n    {\n      \"kind\": \"dependency\",\n      \"coordinate\": \"javax.servlet:servlet-api:2.4\",\n      \"scope\": \"testImplementation\",\n      \"reason\": \"The artifact POM marks servlet-api as provided, so Gradle will not bring javax.servlet.* onto the test classpath transitively; existing Jackrabbit WebDAV coverage exercises servlet-facing classes such as AbstractWebdavServlet, WebdavRequestImpl, WebdavResponseImpl, InputContextImpl, and OutputContextImpl.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The reported native-image failures are assertion failures in existing AbstractLocatorFactory tests, so local Gradle/Native Image verification must still confirm whether behavior changed between 1.5.0 and 2.0-beta4 rather than treating setup as the root cause.\",\n    \"No Docker service appears necessary; the library can be covered with in-process WebDAV/XML/request-response tests rather than a live WebDAV server.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_056415668624bc0e016a4276dd39048194a6a642258fbc369b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1816, "output": 1313, "cacheRead": 23552, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 26681, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782740682184, "responseId": "resp_056415668624bc0e016a4276cb1b048194bece2b2270e88af6"}, "toolResults": []}
